\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170214/00176_081.html</a> (東方日報)"},{"pid":"a8d4c53ced7200c7d0d8c00c2e3b411ba6efdb69","tid":119541,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:40:22.000Z","msg":"兩岸:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 美國國防部官員透露，近日在太平洋執行任務的「卡爾文森號」航母戰鬥群將駛進南海，艦隊或將航行至中國南沙或西沙島礁的12海里內。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009259414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009259414&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0d540458\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009259414&h=256de4bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009259414</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00178_010.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3d17083e\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_010.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549149&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549149%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=828c816a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549149%26target%3D2&h=93608eef\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549149&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 江蘇南京一艘遠洋貨輪「聯合女神號」去年底在印度霍爾迪亞港卸貨後，據報因船東公司拖欠國外油商款項被印度扣押至今，船上23名船員被困當地48天且被拖欠共150萬元人民幣工資。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00178_001.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1eb11298\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_001.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 中國載人航天工程辦公室宣佈，中國自行研製的「天舟一號」貨運太空船安全運抵海南文昌航天發射場，計劃在今年四月中下旬由「長征七號」運載火箭發射升空，為「天宮二號」空間實驗室補充物資。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549152&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549152%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0f22e275\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549152%26target%3D2&h=e9a6d03a\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549152&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 陜西省榆林市人社局就業科科長徐彥江隱瞞已婚事實包養一名劉姓女子，後來徐彥江遭該名女子公開其嫖娼及利用職權收受賄款，目前市紀委已經介入調查。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009262269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009262269&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=49c1aa18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009262269&h=3ff65074\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009262269</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_014.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00178_014.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3b81aee6\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_014.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 台北一輛載有40多名乘客的賞櫻旅遊巴在回程時失控翻落邊坡，車頂被削，多人拋出車外，造成32人死亡，另有12人受傷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009256778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009256778&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e9a48b11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00013%2F1487009256778&h=9027ace2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00013/1487009256778</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_006.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00178_006.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1ac94e9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_006.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549170&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549170%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4834f6b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549170%26target%3D2&h=6894a1dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549170&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170214/19927833?_ga=1.134025550.1316658954.1419942048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927833%3F_ga%3D1.134025550.1316658954.1419942048&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ddb4158c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170214%2F19927833%3F_ga%3D1.134025550.1316658954.1419942048&h=02afc0b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170214/19927833?_ga=1.134025550.1316658954.1419942048</a> (蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 廈門地鐵二號線施工現場出現意外，鑽挖式隧道在減壓過程起火，3人嚴重燒傷身亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_031.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00178_031.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=78b5c7a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00178_031.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549161&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549161%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6bbffcd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549161%26target%3D2&h=280d992f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549161&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)"},{"pid":"03d6cfad69109ec57440ec08499039a25c5920e2","tid":119541,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T23:40:33.000Z","msg":"國際:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 東非國家索馬里、埃塞俄比亞與肯尼亞正面臨罕見乾旱，農作物收成銳減，超過1100萬人受到饑荒威脅，急需各方救援。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549140&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549140%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f3e0f8a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549140%26target%3D2&h=14f58407\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549140&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 就美國總統特朗普簽下行政命令興建美墨圍牆一事，有約二萬名民眾於首都墨西哥城示威，要求特朗普尊重他們的國家和移民。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00180_003.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1f460b33\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_003.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 南韓執政的新國家黨決定將黨名更改為自由韓國黨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549134&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549134%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c618df39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549134%26target%3D2&h=b1814451\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549134&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 於2009年澳洲悉尼華人林暋一家五口滅門案中，案中53歲疑兇、林暋的妹夫謝連斌（Robert Xie）被裁定五項謀殺罪成，他被判處五次終身監禁，同期執行。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_021.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00180_021.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=580a3e7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_021.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 法國阿爾卑斯山發生雪崩，事故造成至少9人被埋，當中4人死亡，救援人員正加緊搜救。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_029.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00180_029.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=552773cf\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_029.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 美國北加州連日暴雨令奧羅維爾水庫水位暴漲，位於奧羅維爾鎮附近的美國最高水壩由於其緊急泄洪道出現巨型缺口有倒塌危險，當局下令住在水壩下游的居民緊急疏散，近20萬人受影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00014/1487009269648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00014%2F1487009269648&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a12a88ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170214%2Fs00014%2F1487009269648&h=853278f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170214/s00014/1487009269648</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170214%2F00180_017.html&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3bd31efb\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170214/00180_017.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1549119&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549119%26target%3D2&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=9581951e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1549119%26target%3D2&h=17c3e082\" target=\"_blank\">h